# Ticketing system (Jira ) Description
This project demonstrates handling IT support tickets using jira . It includes identifying problems , providing solutions, documenting issues and escalating tickets when necessary.

Steps taken 
identified the problem _ checked the ticket details in jira to understand the issue.
Provided solution _ Applied the fix or workaround for the reported problem in jira .
Documented the issue _ Recorded the problem, steps taken and resolution in jira.
Forwarded to higher _ level support  _ escalated tickets in jira that couldnt be resolved.
